## Limitations

This report is based on available data and publications up to October 2023. The rapidly evolving nature of the pandemic and its impacts means that new findings may emerge that could alter the current understanding. Additionally, the focus on English-language sources may limit the inclusion of perspectives from non-English speaking regions. Further research is needed to explore the long-term impacts of the pandemic on different demographic groups and educational systems globally.